                                                                               <article id="einstein"><h2>Albert Einstein</h2>
                                                                                     <p>Albert Einstein (1879–1955)
                                                                                     Famous for: Theory of Relativity, photoelectric effect, contributions to quantum mechanics.</p>
                                                                                             <br>
                                                                                             <b>Key Inventions/Discoveries:</b>
                                                                                               <ul>
                                                                                                   <li><b>Theory of Special Relativity:</b> Revolutionized the way we understand space, time, and energy.</li>

                                                                                                   <li><b>E=mc²:</b> Formula that shows the relationship between energy and mass.</li>

                                                                                                   <li><b>Photoelectric Effect:</b> This helped establish quantum theory and earned him the Nobel Prize in Physics in 1921</li>
                                                                                                       </ul>
                                                                                                             <h3>More Information:</h3>
                                                                                                                     <a href="https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Albert_Einstein" target="_blank">click here to learn more.</a></p>
                                                                                                                         </article>
                                                                                                                             <article id="edison"><h2>Thomas Alva Edison</h2>
                                                                                                                                 <p>Thomas Edison (1847–1931)

                                                                                                                                 Famous for:Inventions in electricity, motion pictures, and sound recording.</p>
                                                                                                                                       <br>

                                                                                                                                       <b>Key Inventions/Discoveries:</b>     
                                                                                                                                       <ul>
                                                                                                                                       <em><li><b>Light Bulb:</b> Edison is often credited with inventing the practical incandescent light bulb, although he improved upon earlier designs.</li>

                                                                                                                                       <li><b>Phonograph:</b> Edison invented the phonograph in 1877, a device capable of recording and reproducing sound, considered the first true sound recording device.</li>

                                                                                                                                       <li><b>Motion Pictures:</b>Edison helped develop the first commercially successful motion picture camera and projector, contributing greatly to the film industry.</li>

                                                                                                                                       <li><b>Electric Power Distribution:</b> He created one of the first electric power stations, helping to develop the infrastructure for electric lighting.</li></em></ul>
                                                                                                                                             <h3> more information:</h3>
                                                                                                                                               <a href="https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thomas_Edison" target="_blank">click here to learn more</a></p>
